Lectures transmission of knowledge of the technology education didactics. Discussed the best didactic teaching technology education solutions. Students compose together a number of independent tasks. As a result of subject students are able to prepare lessons and conduct the technology education in teaching on a high level.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the subject is to enable students to acquire the knowledge and skills to carry out technology education studies classes. Teaching through subject is to achieve the student's willingness to carry out a high level of technology education lessons.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1. Knows and is able to use the technology education syllabus. 2. Is able to create technology education lesson plans, problem learning, student competition questions, digital teaching material. 3. Is able to create a work program for the teacher.  4. Is able to integrate syllabus learning contents with the necessary competencies.  5. Writing and analyzing the narrative of "Technology Education Being a Teacher". 6. Drawing up the plan of technology education of teaching physical learning environment (classrooms). 7. Draw up a portfolio. 8. Is able to write a report on the basis of foreign literature. 9. Knows and is able to carry out the technology education of teaching lessons.
